A^TA=I
\begin{align} A^TA=I\Rightarrow\sum_aA_{ai}A_{aj}&=\delta_{ij} \\ \sum_aX_{ai}X_{aj}=\sum_aA_{ak_i}A_{ak_j}&=\delta_{k_ik_j}=\delta_{ij}\Rightarrow X^TX=I, \\ \end{align}
\delta_{k_ik_j}=\delta_{ij}
